data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bedroom, 2.75 bath, 2863 sf home w/ both a bonus room & rec room downstairs & 4 bedrooms including primary bedroom w/ private 3/4 bathroom.  New paint inside & out, new floors/carpets, and bathroom cabinets/countertops. Large fully fenced back yard w/ fire pit, play structure, and shed.  Detached deep 2 car garage w/ shop possibilities & more space to park "toys" as well as gravel RV parking on side of garage.  Vaulted ceilings welcome you home to the living area w/ separate dining room & semi-open kitchen. Composite back deck for all of your back yard fun.  Wired for generator w/ newer roof too. Amazing opportunity to have space & a beautiful updated home. $10k Seller credit to Buyer at closing for full price offer!
